  "short_description": "Tactics algorithm RPG with a pop world view stretched out by the \"Three Fairies of Light\"! While Hoppin' & flappin' the world of quarter view, can the three fairies defeat Cirno by mastering \"Tactics system\"? Contrary to its pop appearance, it's a large-volume RPG with plenty of elements to play!",
